uad.php?player=88139&includeref=dynamic Scarlets profile]\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Ford, Dale}}\n[[Category:Welsh rugby union players]]\n[[Category:Scarlets players]]\n[[Category:1991 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Rugby union players from Swansea]]\n\n\n{{Wales-rugbyunion-bio-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{short description|Welsh rugby union player}}\n{{BLP unsourced|date=March 2020}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=November 2012}}\n{{Infobox rugby biography\n| name = Dale Ford\n| image = \n| birth_name = Dale Ford\n| birth_date = {{birth date and age|1991|12|16|df=y}}\n| birth_place = [[Swansea]], [[Wales]]\n| height = {{convert|178|cm|ftin|abbr=on}}\n| weight = {{convert|85|kg|stlb|abbr=on}}\n| nickname = \n| school =\n| university =\n| relatives = \n| ru_currentposition = \n| ru_currentteam = [[Carmarthen Quins RFC|Carmarthen Quins]]\n| ru_position = [[Rugby union positions#Full-back|Full-back]]<br />[[Rugby union positions#Wing|Wing]]\n| ru_clubyears = 2008-2013<br/>2013-2015<br/>2015-\n| ru_proclubs = [[Llanelli RFC|Llanelli]]<br/>[[Neath RFC|Neath]]<br/>[[Carmarthen Quins RFC|Carmarthen Quins]]\n| ru_clubcaps = 62<br/>23 <br/>11 \n| ru_clubpoints = (142)<br/>(50)<br/>(10)\n| ru_clubupdate =  21:59 10 December 2015 (UTC)\n| ru_years = \n| ru_province = [[Scarlets]]\n| ru_provinceyears = 2009-2013\n| ru_provincecaps = 9\n| ru_provincepoints = (3)\n| ru_provinceupdate =  21:59 10 December 2015 (UTC)\n| ru_nationalyears = <br/>2011\n| ru_nationalteam = [[Wales national under-18 rugby union team|Wales U18]]<br/>[[Wales national under-20 rugby union team|Wales U20]]\n| ru_nationalcaps = <br/>3\n| ru_nationalpoints = <br/>(5)\n| ru_ntupdate =  21:49 10 December 2015 (UTC)\n}}\n'''Dale Ford''' (born 16 December 1991) is a Welsh [[rugby union]] player. A winger, he plays club rugby for the Welsh team the [[Carmarthen Quins RFC|Carmarthen Quins]] having previously played for [[Llanelli RFC|Llaneli]] and [[Neath RFC|Neath]].\n\n==External links==\n* [http://www.scarlets.co.u